<body>
<div class="container-fluid p-0">
    <header class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-center py-4 mb-4 border-bottom">
        <a href="/" class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3 mb-md-0 me-md-auto link-body-emphasis text-decoration-none">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="fill: rgb(238, 255, 0);"><path d="M6.995 12c0 2.761 2.246 5.007 5.007 5.007s5.007-2.246 5.007-5.007-2.246-5.007-5.007-5.007S6.995 9.239 6.995 12zM11 19h2v3h-2zm0-17h2v3h-2zm-9 9h3v2H2zm17 0h3v2h-3zM5.637 19.778l-1.414-1.414 2.121-2.121 1.414 1.414zM16.242 6.344l2.122-2.122 1.414 1.414-2.122 2.122zM6.344 7.759 4.223 5.637l1.415-1.414 2.12 2.122zm13.434 10.605-1.414 1.414-2.122-2.122 1.414-1.414z"></path></svg>
            <span class="fs-1 ms-2">AccWeather</span>
        </a>

        <ul class="nav nav-pills">
            <li class="nav-item"><a href="/" class="nav-link">Home</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a href="/Features" class="nav-link">Features</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a href="/FAQs" class="nav-link active">FAQs</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a href="/About" class="nav-link">About</a></li>
        </ul>
    </header>
</div>
<div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header text-center">
                    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                                <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                                    What is AccWeather?
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    AccWeather is a weather application that provides real-time weather updates, forecasts, and location-based weather information. It offers features such as interactive maps, customizable alerts, and historical weather data.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                                    How can I use the application?
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    To use AccWeather, simply enter your location into the search box on the homepage. The application will provide you with the current weather conditions and forecasts for your area. You can also explore additional features such as weather maps and historical data.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                                    Is there a mobile app available?
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    Currently, AccWeather is available as a web application. We are working on developing mobile apps for iOS and Android, which will be released in the near future. Stay tuned for updates!
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                                    How accurate is the weather information?
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    AccWeather uses data from reputable weather APIs to provide accurate and up-to-date weather information. However, weather forecasts are inherently uncertain and can change based on new data and conditions.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFive">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
                                    How can I contact support?
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    If you need assistance or have any questions, you can contact our support team via the contact form on our website or by emailing support@accweather.com. We aim to respond to all inquiries within 24 hours.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.6/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-oBqDVmMz4fnFO9fJ2wLAXqgrXcL2fA5F7h0s0GbVI3JhbT4QG8eVQCO/BYSAEk47S" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
